      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>A varculak imparts the leech @Compendium[sfrpg.rules.O5GDQUKPCJ9Zbnfj]{Critical Hit Effect} to any melee weapon it wields, but the saving throw DC is 10 + the varculak&rsquo;s level + its Strength modifier, and the duration of the effect is 1d4 rounds. In addition, when a creature fails its save against this leech critical hit effect, the varculak regains a number of Hit Points equal to half its CR or level (minimum 0). If the weapon already has a critical hit effect, the varculak must choose which to apply on a critical hit.</p>"
